## 模拟

根据题意进行模拟即可。

代码：

* []

```Java
class Solution {
    public String mergeAlternately(String s1, String s2) {
        int n = s1.length(), m = s2.length(), i = 0, j = 0;
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        while (i < n || j < m) {
            if (i < n) sb.append(s1.charAt(i++));
            if (j < m) sb.append(s2.charAt(j++));
        }
        return sb.toString();
    }
}
```

